  <data name="lblInstructions.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Use the buttons on the left to get around the system:

- Bookings: make and manage customer bookings
- Find Booking: search for a booking and cancel it
- Screenings: see what films are showing and when
- Customers: look up customer details
- Films: add and edit films (managers only)
- Screens: set up screens and seating (managers only)
- Food: manage food and drink items (managers only)
- Reports: view sales reports (managers only)
- Logs: view a history of actions taken in the system (managers only)

Use the Log out button at the bottom when you are finished.</value>
